classes.description: Data source for the TibcoCloudTable view. This class should encapsulate all logic for fetching and manipulating the displayed data (including sorting, pagination, and filtering).
classes.rawdescription:
Data source for the TibcoCloudTable view. This class should
encapsulate all logic for fetching and manipulating the displayed data
(including sorting, pagination, and filtering).

methods.name: connect
methods.description: Connect this data source to the table. The table will only update when the returned stream emits new items.

jsdoctags.comment: A stream of the items to be rendered.

methods.name: disconnect
methods.description: Called when the table is being destroyed. Use this function, to clean up any open connections or free any held resources that were set up during connect.

methods.name: getPagedData
methods.description: Paginate the data (client-side). If you're using server-side pagination, this would be replaced by requesting the appropriate data from the server.

methods.name: getSortedData
methods.description: Sort the data (client-side). If you're using server-side sorting, this would be replaced by requesting the appropriate data from the server.
